title: 106: Post Workout Macros, MindPump Origins, Skyscraper Daredevils & Sport Obsessions
description: It is Q&A time once again! Sal, Adam & Justin answer your questions about what to eat after working out, how they met and decided to start MindPump, their thoughts on people who take selfies while balancing on the edge of the roofs of skyscrapers and their favorite sports.
